Great experience
Jan 2023 • Friends
It is about 15-20 minutes from Da Nang's center. We paid 20,000 dong each for the first cave near the Marble Mountain's entrance and 40,000 dong per person to go to the top plus 15,000 dong for each tide for the elevator. We climbed the highest peak and went to see the other caves. There's a lot to see, so you could spend the entire day exploring the area.
