Hidden gem
Jan 2020 • Family
This is an amazing area to explore. From the outside it’s hard to imagine all the intricate caves and sights inside. If you are fit and enable there are many caves and areas to explore here. No need to go up and down the lift.

It costs about 50,000 VND by grab from Da Nang (10 mins)
