Worth every step!
Jan 2023 • Couples
Marble mountains is a fantastic area to explore Asian religion and hike at the same time.It involves strenuous climbs up many stairs, especially to see the different vantage points, but it’s worth every step! The main cave with a Buddha statue and sunlight shining in from about 30 m high opening in the ceiling will remain with you far longer than you think. Highly recommend!
